   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Volatility\n",
    "$$ \\sigma_p^2 = \\sum_{i=1}^{k} \\sum_{j=1}^{k} w_i w_j \\sigma_{i, j} $$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Return\n",
    "$$ R_p = \\sum_{i=1}^{k} w_i R_i  = w^T R$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Quadratic form:\n",
    "$$ min: \\frac{1}{2} w^T \\sum w$$\n",
    "$$ s.t.: w^T R = r_0$$\n",
    "$$ w^T 1 = 1$$\n",
    "$$ w \\geq 0 $$"
